.description
Bon Appetit is a recipe database manager that automates recipe collections
and allows for far more flexibility than regular index cards.  You can
search for recipes by title, keyword, or ingredient.  You can import
recipes in BonAppetit's own format or 3 popular MS-DOS formats, so you can
quickly build a recipe collection.  Includes complete recipe utilities and
24 recipes to get you started.  New features include recipe browsing, mass
export, less cryptic error messages, and many bug fixes.  
